title: Cannot login to Aura
description: I'm getting an error message when trying to log into Aura with my 3DS credentials. The page just refreshes without logging me in.
resolutionSummary: Clear browser cache and cookies. Issue was related to stored authentication tokens.

title: Aura giving incorrect CATIA information
description: When I ask Aura about CATIA V6 features it provides outdated information from V5. The responses don't match current documentation.
resolutionSummary: Updated knowledge base with latest CATIA V6 documentation. Aura responses now reflect current version.

title: Request: Add SIMULIA integration to Aura
description: Would like Aura to be able to answer questions about SIMULIA workflows and provide direct links to SIMULIA documentation.

title: Aura very slow response times
description: Aura is taking 30+ seconds to respond to simple questions. This is significantly slower than usual.
resolutionSummary: Identified server load issue during peak hours. Implemented load balancing solution.

title: Error when asking about employee directory
description: Getting 'Service Unavailable' error when asking Aura to lookup employee information. Works for other queries.
resolutionSummary: Directory service integration was down. Restored connection and verified functionality.

title: Training session for DELMIA team
description: Our DELMIA team needs training on how to effectively use Aura for manufacturing-related questions.

title: Aura not recognizing department names
description: When I mention 'CATIA Development' Aura doesn't understand it's a department and gives generic responses.
resolutionSummary: Added department recognition to Aura's entity detection. Now properly identifies organizational units.

title: Mobile access to Aura not working
description: Aura works fine on desktop but mobile browser version is not loading properly on my iPhone.

title: Feature request: Voice commands for Aura
description: Would be great if Aura could accept voice input for hands-free operation during design work.

title: Aura returning partial responses
description: Aura responses are getting cut off mid-sentence. Seems to happen with longer technical explanations.
resolutionSummary: Identified token limit issue in response generation. Increased response buffer and added continuation handling.

title: Cannot find Aura documentation
description: Looking for comprehensive user guide for Aura but can't locate it on the intranet.
resolutionSummary: Provided direct links to Aura documentation portal and added bookmark to user's intranet favorites.

title: Aura integration with Outlook calendar
description: Request to integrate Aura with Outlook so it can help schedule meetings and check availability.
